    <h1>Jokes API Documentation</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Jokes API</p>
    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Get a Random Joke</h2>
      <p>Returns a randomly selected joke from the available jokes.</p>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code><span class="get-method">GET</span> BASE_URL/api/random</code>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
  "id": 55,
  "jokeText": "I told my wife she was drawing her eyebrows too high. She looked surprised.",
  "jokeType": "Puns",
}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Filter Jokes</h2>
      <p>Returns a list of jokes filtered by type .</p>
      <p><strong>Query Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <code>type</code>: The type of activity to filter by. Choice of
          <code>Science , Puns, Wordplay, Math, Food, Movies, Sports</code>.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">GET</span>
            BASE_URL/api/filter?type=Science</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "jokeText": "Why don't scientists trust atoms? Because they make up everything.",
        "jokeType": "Science"
    },
    {
        "id": 6,
        "jokeText": "How do you organize a space party? You planet!",
        "jokeType": "Science"
    }
]</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Get Jokes by id</h2>
      <p>Returns the joke with the specified id.</p>
      <p><strong>URL Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>id</code>: The unique id of the joke.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">GET</span> BASE_URL/api/jokes/15</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
  "id": 15,
  "jokeText": "I'm reading a book about anti-gravity. It's impossible to put down!",
  "jokeType": "Science"
}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Insert Jokes</h2>
      <p>Insert a new joke .</p>
      <p><strong>Body Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>type</code>: The type of joke to insert.</li>
        <li><code>text</code>: Joke that will get inserted.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code><span class="get-method">POST</span> BASE_URL/api/jokes</code>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
    "message": "Joke added successfully at id=98"
}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Edit a Joke</h2>
      <p>Edit already existing joke .</p>
      <p><strong>URL Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>id</code>: Id of job that is going to updated.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Body Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>type</code>: The type of joke .</li>
        <li><code>text</code>: Joke text that will get updated.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">PUT</span> BASE_URL/api/jokes/98</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
      "id": 98,
      "jokeText": "Why was the mobile phone wearing glasses?... Because it lost its contacts",
      "jokeType": "Tech"
    }</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Partial Edit a Joke</h2>
      <p>Edit already existing joke .</p>
      <p><strong>URL Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>id</code>: Id of job that is going to updated.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Body Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>type</code> (optional): The type of joke .</li>
        <li><code>text</code> (optional): Joke text that will get updated.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">PUT</span> BASE_URL/api/jokes/98</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
        "id": 98,
        "jokeText": "Why was the mobile phone wearing glasses?... Because it lost its contacts",
        "jokeType": "Tech"
      }</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Delete a Joke</h2>
      <p>Delete already existing joke using id .</p>
      <p><strong>URL Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><code>id</code>: Id of job that is going to deleted.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">DELETE</span> BASE_URL/api/jokes/56</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>{
          messgae:`Joke with id=56 is deleted.`
        }</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Delete all Jokes</h2>
      <p>Delete all joke with help of key .</p>
      <p><strong>Query Parameters:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <code>key</code>: User Key which authorized to perform this action.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="example">
        <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
        <div class="request">
          <code
            ><span class="get-method">DELETE</span>
            BASE_URL/api/jokes?key=key_here</code
          >
        </div>
        <p><strong>Example Response:</strong></p>
        <div class="response">
          <pre><code>
          {
            message:`Delete action completed successfully`
          }
        </code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="endpoint">
      <h2>Reset all Jokes</h2>
      <p>Reset jokes using key .</p>
      <p><strong>Query Parameters:</strong></p>
